<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM13.8">
<l>uḷḷē yuruki naivēṉai uḷaḷō vilaḷō veṉṉāta</l>
<l>koḷḷai koḷḷik kuṟumpaṉaik kōvart taṉaṉaik kaṇṭakkāl</l>
<l>koḷḷum payaṉoṉ ṟillāta koṅkai taṉṉaik kiḻaṅkōṭum</l>
<l>aḷḷip paṟittiṭṭavaṉ mārvi leṟinteṉṉa ḻalaitīr vēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When I see the Cattle-Grower, the Mischievous robber,</l>
<l>who does not wonder whether I, who am wasting away melting inside, am alive or not!</l>
<l>I shall end my [feeling of] burning by grabbing and plucking out [my] breasts</l>
<l rend="indent">that do not have the least use one [can] have</l>
<l>From [their] roots and throwing [them] at His chest!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
